title: Jokic, Embiid, and Tyson's Ear Gummies
description:
Jalen & Jacoby break down the battle of the Bigs - Jokic vs Embiid. Nuggets come out on too, but has it shifted perception around MVP? Plus! A bunch of huge nights across the NBA: KAT goes for 60, Trae has 46, Chef Curry was cooking with Dray back in the Lineup, and LeBron was big mad vs Toronto. All that, and we got Mike Tyson's ear gummies and "White Men Can't Jump" info. Tap in, with J&J.
